RELEASED
----------


AR-15 556/9mm/22lr pretty much every caliber 
- Tons of places for purchase and many different variants.
	- Super Safety
		- Requires low shelf lower
		- Trigger Cut
		- Crossbolt, push button safety

	- Atrius Super Selector
		- Requires low shelf lower
		- 3 position traditional safety selector

	- ASDesigns ARC
		- Requires low shelf lower
		- Trigger Cut
		- 3 position traditional safety selector

	- Arizona Regulator
		- Drop in
		- Lower Shelf doesn't matter
		- 3 position traditional safety selector

	- Kabuto/TURD/ARSS15
		- Drop in
		- Most have 3D printed parts, but the ARSS15 by bssquirts is all metal
		- 3 position traditional safety selector

	- Rarebreed FRT-15
		- Cassette style trigger

	- Delta Team Tactical FRT-15L3
		- Cassette style trigger

	- Dairyland Defense FRT-15
		- Cassette style trigger

	- Partisan Triggers The Disruptor
	
- AR9 and AR22 set ups requires more specific details, please research that

AR-10 
- Grey Market Research has super safety sets for AR-10.

AK 
- Tons of places for purchase
- Normally 2 position, but 3 position is possible but requires a decent amount of work and 

HK MP5 platform 
- Tons of places for purchase. 
- There are two versions, the current released version is a separate lower that accepts AR-15 FCG, $D printed Leber or a metal lower from ASDesgins
- Rarebreed has a lower in development that uses a standard MP5 lower.

Steyr AUG 
- Hole drilled into stock is required.

Springfield Kuna 
- Requires a separate lower and trip from Nexus Firearms, this allows for either Rarebreed or super safety function and CZ EVO Magpul Pmags capability
- ASDesgins is also working on a lower.

SIG MCX platform 
- There is a trip bar you can install in the upper which allows usage of a Rarebreed. 
- ASDesigns has a separate trip in the lower that allows for super safeties and their ARC selector.

Taurus TX22 
- Tons of places for purchase.
- Don't get it from FFT, it's very expensive and considered the "gen 1" variant of the trip
- The new versions of the trip is much easier on the internals
- There are weighed striker assemblies which allows for suppressor and subsonic ammo use

Glock platform 
- Tons of places for purchase.

S&W M&P platform 
- Was available for sale by Freedom Finger Triggers, but currently they are waiting for an ATF letter. 
- There are others that sell the same design

1911/2011
- A few of places for purchase.

Beretta 90 series 
- Released by Griffith Guns.

Canik 
- Released by gforcecnc.

PSA Rock 5.7
- A few of places for purchase.

B&T APC series
- East Valley Tactical has a service that allows lowers to work with the Rarebreed trigger and uses their safety to allow usage in the OEM lower. 
- Asdesigns is working on it as a separate lower to allow function with a super safety or ARC selector, this is not yet released.

B&T GHM9
- East Valley Tactical has a service that allows lowers to work with the Rarebreed trigger and uses their safety to allow usage in the OEM lower. 
- Asdesigns is working on it as a separate lower to allow function with a super safety or ARC selector, this is not yet released.

B&T SPC9
- East Valley Tactical has a service that allows lowers to work with the Rarebreed trigger and uses their safety to allow usage in the OEM lower. 
- Asdesigns is working on it as a separate lower to allow function with a super safety or ARC selector, this is not yet released.

PSA JAKL platform 
- Trip Released by Asdesigns.

Kriss Vector
- Released by Duality Arms Co, Currently not able to be purchased due to issues they are having with payment processors.

JTS M12AK 
- A few of places for purchase.

Ruger 10/22
- Advanced Reset Tech makes the device but Mars Trigger has a pre order for a different design.

FN SCAR 16/17 
- Requires a separate lower by Imperial Arms to allow for AR FCG, it also requires a trip and the bolt modified to use the Rarebreed FRT. 
- Asdesigns is working on a separate lower which allows for super safe and ARC.

VZ61 
- Requires a separate lower that allows for AR FCG.
- There are also people working on an FRT in the standard lower.

Keltec P50 
- Requires the ST-50 FCG and trip from stuff and things inc.


IN DEVELOPMENT
----------


AP53 
- Asdesigns is working on it. 
- Requires Seperate lower.

HK G3/91
- Asdesigns is working on it.
- Requires Seperate lower.

BRN-180
- Asdesigns is working on it.
- Requires Seperate lower.

CMMG Dissent platform 
- Asdesigns is working on it.

Stribog platform 
- Some people have got this to work with a super safety and ARC with Lingle lower. This seems to require a cut in the upper
- Asdesigns is working on a different option, which requires a seperate lower

CZ Scorpion
- Nexus Firearms is working on it to allow function with the Rarebreed trigger.

Beretta Cx4 
- Seems to be by Brello Solutions.

CZ BREN 2 
- Nexus Firearms is working on it to allow function with the Rarebreed trigger, this is a separate lower.

SIG P320
- There seems to be two solutions for this, an anon in the thread has a working model that's selectable and also is waiting for an ATF letter. 
- The other solution is teased by Duality Arms Co.

Ruger PC Charger 
- Pre-order available by Mars Trigger.

Ruger PC Carbine 
- Pre-order available by Mars Trigger.

FN PS90 
- There seems to be multiple solutions for this, Duality Arms Co is working on a solution
- Dorin Technologies which would be unveiled during SHOT Show 2026.
- 2 position solution exists by @BSquaredMfg

FN M249S 
- Asdesigns is working on it.

B&T TP9 
- Duality Arms Co is working on a solution

VZ58 
- An anon in the thread is working on it, 3 position as well.

FAL 
- This was mentioned in a thread, no public information is released.

Matador Arms AR9 uppers
- Matador Arms is working on a trip to allow for super safe usage.

SKS 
- Hush Holsters are working on it.
